    <constraint source="ADR-015">Telemetry/log payloads carry: handlerName, sessionId, fileCount, durationMs ONLY. NEVER file content, summary text, classifiedDocType per-file (aggregate counts only).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Per-task BFF publish-size measurement; expect ≤+0.1 MB.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-033">Returns a SINGLE `ToolResult`; does NOT stream. Memory tools are non-streaming per ADR-033 amendment.</constraint>
    <constraint source="architecture">§3.2 — reads T2 only; no writes. Always-on per §8.2 when session has files.</constraint>
    <constraint source="architecture">§8.1 — return shape matches schema verbatim (including recentlyDiscussed + citationsReferenced fields).</constraint>
    <constraint source="architecture">§2 P3 — trust framing applies to the `precomputedSummary` field description.</constraint>
